 like the Compound Creator, but its flame makes the hot formulas too (H2SO4, glucose, rust, silica).\n",color:"black"},{text:"TUBE RACK",color:"aqua",bold:true},{text:": click holding a tube to shelf it (6 slots, visible!), click empty-handed to take one back.",color:"black"}],[{text:"Anomalous appendix\n\n",color:"dark_red",bold:true},{text:"SCP-294",color:"black",bold:true},{text:": the drink dispenser. Two Quarters buys any compound - or a Coffee, Hot Chocolate, Estus... or god.\n",color:"black"},{text:"SCP-009",color:"red",bold:true},{text:": red ice. Freezes water. Do not touch it. Safe handling procedures exist; personnel are expected to work them out.\n",color:"black"},{text:"SCP-999",color:"gold",bold:true},{text:": orange gel. Drink for joy - clears the ordinary ailments and buys time against the extraordinary ones.\n",color:"black"},{text:"SCP-207",color:"black",bold:true},{text:": some Regular Cola is just cola. Some is not. There is no way to tell.\n",color:"black"},{text:"SCP-148",color:"dark_aqua",bold:true},{text:": telekill alloy - carried, it blocks element radiation.",color:"black"}]]}]
